data.meta_description: Historical map of the Duchy of Lüneburg from Brunswick in the southeast to Hamburg in the northwest, ''Ducatus Luneburgici et Comitatus Dannebergensis'', partly colored copper engraving map by Homann, Nuremberg c. 1730, figural title cartouche, scattered stains in margins, sheet measures 52 x 60 cm
